OL,3,CNI charities facing huge tax bill
OL,5,FHomelessness charities are warning
OL,6,Fthat some services might have to be
OL,7,Freduced following April's hike to
OL,8,FNational Insurance which means
OL,9,Femployers now need to pay 15%.
OL,11,FThis could result in additional costs
OL,12,Frunning into the millions of pounds
OL,13,Ffor the sector, according to its
OL,14,Frepresentative body.
OL,16,FAs a result, it is calling on Stormont
OL,17,Fto provide financial support.
