OL,3,CNI charities facing huge tax bill
OL,5,FMark Baillie from Homeless Connect,
OL,6,Fsaid: "This is just yet another
OL,7,Fchallenge that the sector faces. And
OL,8,Fagain, we are calling on and urging
OL,9,Fthe Department for Communities, the
OL,10,FMinister for Communities and the
OL,11,FExecutive to do everything in their
OL,12,Fpower to ensure that these increased
OL,13,FNational Insurance contribution costs
OL,14,Fare mitigated.
OL,16,F"Because if they're not, there could
OL,17,Fbe very serious consequences for
OL,18,Fpeople who are experiencing
OL,19,Fhomelessness right now and for people
OL,20,Fwho are on the margins."
