OL,5,FThese fears are echoed by a First
OL,6,FHousing, a charity that employs more
OL,7,Fthan 125 people across Northern
OL,8,FIreland.
OL,10,FOne of the services it runs is a youth
OL,11,Faccommodation service in Londonderry
OL,12,Fknown as Jefferson Court which houses
OL,13,F25 young people who are at risk of
OL,14,Fhomelessness.
