OL,3,CNI charities facing huge tax bill
OL,5,FBut over the year, the charity
OL,6,Festimates that the National Insurance
OL,7,Fchanges will add nearly #200,000 to
OL,8,Fits tax bill, which means it might
OL,9,Fhave to reassess how it allocates its
OL,10,Fmoney to services such as Jefferson
OL,11,FCourt.
OL,13,FEileen Best said: "If we weren't here,
OL,14,FI believe that it would cost the
OL,15,Fpublic purse much, much more because
OL,16,Four services impact on emergency
OL,17,Fservices, the juvenile justice system,
OL,18,Fthe police, and on A&E.
