OL,5,F"All those services at the moment are
OL,6,Fstretched with their own budgets and
OL,7,Fit would become an even greater
OL,8,Fcrisis."
OL,10,FThe Department for Communities said:
OL,11,F"Minister Lyons has repeatedly
OL,12,Fstressed the need to make the
OL,13,Fstrategic shift to homelessness
OL,14,Fprevention.
OL,16,F"The Northern Ireland Housing
OL,17,FExecutive will now have a dedicated
OL,18,Fhomeless prevention budget beginning
OL,19,Fwith an additional #2.5million this
OL,20,Fyear ring-fenced for the strategic
OL,21,Fprevention of homelessness.
